&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a pharmacist to join our pharmacy team at Basildon Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic pharmacist with excellent clinical and managerial skills to work as the Lead Pharmacist in Critical Care, Theatres and Surgery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The newly merged Mid and South Essex trust means that you will be working closely with your specialist peers at Southend and Broomfield Hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAnna ManJob titleLead Pharmacist for Clinical and Cardiothoracic ServicesEmail addressanna.man@btuh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
